OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784629107
OL,3,CAbandoned monkey rescued on bus
OL,4,Cnicknamed 'Oyster'
OL,6,FA monkey who was left inside a cage
OL,7,Fand covered with a laundry bag has
OL,8,Fbeen found abandoned on a London bus.
OL,10,FThe marmoset was found on a route 302
OL,11,Fbus, travelling between Mill Hill
OL,12,FBroadway Station and Kensal Rise, on
OL,13,FFriday morning (17 July).
OL,15,FThe bus driver discovered the primate
OL,16,Fafter getting up to help a mum with
OL,17,Fher buggy because the laundry bag was
OL,18,Fsticking out of the luggage bay and
OL,19,Fblocking the way.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784629107
OL,3,CAbandoned monkey rescued on bus
OL,4,Cnicknamed 'Oyster'
OL,6,FAs the driver moved the bag, the
OL,7,Fmonkey inside started chirping and
OL,8,Fjumping around, before being taken to
OL,9,Fthe Metroline Bus Depot, at Willesden
OL,10,FBus Station.
OL,12,FThe female monkey has since been
OL,13,Fnicknamed Oyster - after the London
OL,14,Ftravel card.
OL,16,FThe RSPCA has since opened an
OL,17,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784629107
OL,3,CAbandoned monkey rescued on bus
OL,4,Cnicknamed 'Oyster'
OL,6,FThe animal welfare charity fear the
OL,7,Fabandonment is one of many following
OL,8,Fnew legislation that came into force
OL,9,Fin April, which outlines all primates
OL,10,Fkept in England must be licensed.
OL,12,FRSPCA Exotic Animals Expert Evie
OL,13,FButton warned monkeys need lots of
OL,14,Fspace and mental stimulation which
OL,15,Fcan't be met by human company alone
OL,16,Fand is leading owners to give them up.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784629107
OL,3,CAbandoned monkey rescued on bus
OL,4,Cnicknamed 'Oyster'
OL,6,FShe said: "The introduction of primate
OL,7,Flicenses in England is an important
OL,8,Fstep forward for animal welfare,
OL,9,Fhelping to ensure these animals are
OL,10,Fkept in more appropriate conditions,
OL,11,Fbut there is a real concern that
OL,12,Fkeepers who cannot or do not want to
OL,13,Flicense their pet may now instead
OL,14,Fabandon them.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784629107
OL,3,CAbandoned monkey rescued on bus
OL,4,Cnicknamed 'Oyster'
OL,6,F"With the UK Government estimating
OL,7,F5,000 primates being kept as pets in
OL,8,FEngland and our friends at Born Free
OL,9,Freporting very little uptake of the
OL,10,Fnew license system, we're concerned
OL,11,Fabout what has happened to many of
OL,12,Fthese animals."
OL,14,FThe RSPCA is urging those struggling
OL,15,Fto care for a pet or who cannot get a
OL,16,Flicence for any primate they have, to
OL,17,Fspeak to specialists, vets or
OL,18,Fcharities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
