OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784629107
OL,3,CAbandoned monkey rescued on bus
OL,4,Cnicknamed 'Oyster'
OL,6,FOyster the marmoset has now settled
OL,7,Finto a new home at a sanctuary with
OL,8,Fspecialist facilities for primates.
OL,9,FShe will soon be introduced to a new
OL,10,Fmale companion who had been looking
OL,11,Ffor a friend.
OL,13,FThe RSPCA would like to hear from any
OL,14,Fmembers of the public who may have
OL,15,Fseen someone board the bus with the
OL,16,Flaundry bag to contact the appeal line
OL,17,Fon 0300 123 8018.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
